    <section id="during">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="border-bottom: solid; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                <h2>Benefits During Your Career: <span style="font-style: italic;">Protection For Today</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 mx-auto">
                    <div class="panels animated fadeInUp" id="accordion1">
                        <h3 class="accordionheader">
                          <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Medical Plan
                        </h3>
                        <div class="posts">
                            <article>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Covers:</h4>
                                <p>Benefits for medical services, supplies and prescription drugs</p>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">How It Works:</h4>
                                <p>You can use any provider for medical care, although using a Cigna network provider reduces your out-of-pocket costs.</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">In-Network:</span> No cost for preventive care; copays for visit to primary care or specialist ($25), emergency room ($100) and urgent care facility ($100). For other services: $0 annual deductible and out-of-pocket maximum.</li>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>For prescription drugs – $5 generic / $10 preferred brand / $25 non-preferred brand.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">Out-of-Network:</span> $500 (single) / $1,500 (family) deductible, then services covered at 20% of reasonable and customary charges; maximum out of pocket: $1,500 (single) / $4,000(family).</li>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>For prescription drugs: 20% per prescription order or refill.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Who to Contact:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">NBA Players’ Health Service Center:</span> <a href="tel:855-497-6669">855-497-6669</a>, Option 1</li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold"><a href="https://www.cigna.com/" target="_blank">Cigna Website</a></span></li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">Cigna Phone Number: </span><a href="tel:800-244-6224">800-244-6224</a></li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">Your Team Benefits Representative</span></li>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Important Documents:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/n1wp09rs54urk7f/CIGNA_Benefit_Summary.pdf?dl=0" target="_blank">CIGNA Benefit Summary</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="accordionheader">
                          <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Dental Plan
                        </h3>
                        <div class="posts">
                            <article>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Covers:</h4>
                                <p>Benefits for dental services</p>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">How It Works:</h4>
                                <p>You can use any provider for dental care, although using a Cigna network provider reduces your out-of-pocket costs. Out-of-network services are subject to the reasonable and customary allowance.</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">In-Network:</span> $25 (single) / $75 family deductible, preventive paid at 100% (no deductible) then plan pays 90% for basic and 60% for major services, up to $3,000 annual maximum per person. Orthodontia services are covered up to 60% up to a separate $2,000 lifetime maximum per person.</li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">Out of Network:</span> $25 (single) / $75 family deductible, preventive paid at 100% (no deductible) then plan pays 90% for basic and 60% for major services, up to $3,000 annual maximum per person. Orthodontia services are covered up to 60% up to a separate $2,000 lifetime maximum per person.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Who to Contact:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">NBA Players’ Health Service Center:</span> <a href="tel:855-497-6669">855-497-6669</a>, Option 1</li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold"><a href="https://www.cigna.com/" target="_blank">Cigna Website</a></span></li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">Cigna Phone Number:</span> <a href="tel:800-244-6224">800-244-6224</a></li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">Your Team Benefits Representative</span></li>
                                </ul>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="accordionheader">
                          <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Vision Plan
                        </h3>
                        <div class="posts">
                            <article>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Covers:</h4>
                                <p>Benefits for vision exams and eyewear</p>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">How It Works:</h4>
                                <p>You can obtain care from any provider, although benefits are greater if you use an EyeMed network provider.</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">In-Network: </span>Annual exams and lenses in any prescription range are covered in full; allowance provided for eyeglass frames, and contacts.</li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">Out-of-Network: </span>Scheduled reimbursement based on type of service.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Who to Contact:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">NBA Players’ Health Service Center:</span> <a href="tel:855-497-6669">855-497-6669</a>, Option 1</li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold"><a href="http://portal.eyemedvisioncare.com/" target="_blank">EyeMed Website</a></span></li>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">EyeMed Phone:</span> <a href="tel:866-723-0514">866-723-0514</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="accordionheader">
                          <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Life and Accidental Death & Dismemberment (AD&D)
                        </h3>
                        <div class="posts">
                            <article>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Covers:</h4>
                                <p>Financial protection for you and your family (in the event of death or accidental loss)</p>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">How It Works:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Flat $1,000,000 payable to your beneficiary if you die from any cause while covered.</li>
                                    <li>An additional benefit is payable, according to a schedule, if you die or suffer a loss as the result of a covered accident.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Who to Contact:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                <li><span class="font-weight-bold">NBA Players’ Health Service Center:</span> <a href="tel:855-497-6669">855-497-6669</a>, Option 1 then Option 4</li>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="accordionheader">
                          <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Disability Plan
                        </h3>
                        <div class="posts">
                            <article>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">How It Works:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>60% of your contract salary to a maximum weekly benefit of $1,500 ($312,000 maximum lifetime benefit).</li>
                                    <li>Disability payments end on the date you reach the 4-year anniversary of the date your disability, or age 35.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Who to Contact:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><span class="font-weight-bold">NBA Players’ Health Service Center:</span> <a href="tel:855-497-6669">855-497-6669</a>, Option 1 then Option 5</li>
                                </ul>
                               
                            </article>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="accordionheader">
                          <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Tuition Reimbursement Plan
                        </h3>
                        <div class="posts">
                            <article>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Covers:</h4>
                                <p>Reimburses eligible players for fees, textbook and tuition costs for qualifying education programs</p>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">How It Works:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Eligible players may receive up to $33,654 per year (with a lifetime maximum benefit of $101,000).</li>
                                    <li>For players with 3 or more years of NBA service, benefits can be used during and after their playing careers.</li>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Who to Contact:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                    <span class="font-weight-bold">NBA Players’ Health Service Center:</span> <a href="tel:855-497-6669">855-497-6669</a>, Option 3</li>
                                    <li>
                                    <span class="font-weight-bold"><a href="mailto:academicadvisor@nbpa.com">Email an Academic Advisor,</span></a> or call: <a href="tel:212-655-0977">212-655-0977</a></li>
                                </ul>
                                <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Important Documents:</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/0mx4y6ih3dfu7u2/2018%20NBA%20Players%20Tuition%20Plan%20Overview.pdf?dl=0" target="_blank">2018 Plan Overview</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>This summary is intended to provide highlights of your benefits. If there is any conflict between this summary and the applicable legal plan document, as amended, the legal plan document, as amended, shall govern at all times.</p>
